node.accessibility_caption: Photo by REAL TALK KIM on August 11, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'Don't be afraid to start over, you might like your new story'.

node.text: Actually you’ll LOVE your NEW story! NOTHING behind you is better than what’s before you! You’re just apprehensive and scared of the unknowns. But I promise you…. Gods got you and it’s going to be the greatest time of your life! JUMP!! God will either teach you how to fly or catch you if you fall! But you WILL love this new life! 🙏🏽🙏🏽

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by REAL TALK KIM on August 10, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'God is MOVING in your life TONIGHT!!'.

node.text: FACTS!!!! Now, go to sleep! Don’t you worry about a thing! Romans 8:28 God is working ALLLLLLL things together for our good! You’ll see! It’s gonna all come together in your world! Sweet sleep

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by REAL TALK KIM on August 10, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'Some people talk about you because they lost the privilege to talk to you!!! www.realtalkkim.com'.

node.text: Let them keep talking while you keep elevating! Never feel bad for cutting people out of your life that handed you the scissors! Don’t sweat their mess!

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by REAL TALK KIM on August 10, 2021. May be an image of 7 people, people standing and text.

node.text:
I’ve released a whole new line of fabulousness! So much BRAND NEW drip in my store! I have created the  softest cutest sweatsuits, sweatshirts, off the shoulder prophetic tops. Warrior wear is changing lives. 😆😆 Happy Shopping everybody! 
Link in my BIO or www.realtalkkim.com

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by REAL TALK KIM on August 10, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'I used to think I needed closure. Then I realized all I had to do is get up and close the door!'.

node.text: Isn’t it crazy how we will get in the mindset that we need someone else to do for us what God has gifted us the ability to do ourselves!! Rise up! Stop being distracted by irrelevant junk!! Your best is on the other side of your release! Stop looking back! Period!! Let’s go!
